    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The FEA modeling framework demonstrates sufficient credibility for the stated COU. All three QoIs meet pre-specified acceptance bounds. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, gradation 1 vs. required 2) is accepted based on the conservative nature of the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol and the consistency of results across two independent laboratories. The overall evidence package supports regulatory submission use of the FEA predictions.",
